text: Franz Sarnitz (14 April 1919 - 8 December 1992) was an Austrian sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1919 births Category:1992 deaths Category:Austrian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Austria Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
